398
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:09,900
「因此今臨停止春雨不幹」

399
00:24:09,900 --> 00:24:14,060
「That is why the rings have been withheld」

400
00:24:14,060 --> 00:24:17,700
「And the spring rains have not come」

401
00:24:17,700 --> 00:24:19,540
在這裏給我們看見

402
00:24:19,540 --> 00:24:21,940
連續三節裏面

